channel.title: Desperate Help On How To Make A 317 Public/Online
channel.description: This has been frustrating me since Friday.......I have a client and a source so first I try no-ip. So I make the IP tormentedmemories.no-ip.info. Ok, I start the server and my friends try to login through Moparscape and it doesn't work....They try SilabSoft and the same thing occurs. Desperate, I try Hamachi and it still doesn't work.....I put the IP from Hamachi in and stuff and it still didn't work...My friends joined the group and we did everything we were supposed to for Hamachi and No-Ip but it still does not work. I do not know what to do and I need help bad :confused: whoever helps me may be mod on the server, ability to wear fire cape and given a fire cape, and a bunch of rares and customs. Please help!! SERVER: Tormented Memories. TYPE: 317.
